Package: tunly
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1 | gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, openssh-client
Recommends: gir1.2-notify-0.7, libsecret-tools
Maintainer: Ahmed Toulan <thelinuxer@gmail.com>
Description: GNOME tray applet for SSH SOCKS5 tunnels
 Manage multiple named SSH dynamic (SOCKS5) tunnels from the GNOME tray and
 toggle the system proxy in one click. Exclusive model with per-tunnel SSH
 authentication (agent, key file, or password).
